<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Angels_in_Christianity&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Further reading"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/C._A._Patrides" title="C. A. Patrides">Patrides, C. A.</a> (1982). "On the orders of angels". <i>Premises and Motifs in Renaissance Thought and Literature</i>. Princeton. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-691-06505-5" title="Special:BookSources/0-691-06505-5"><bdi>0-691-06505-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=On+the+orders+of+angels&amp;rft.btitle=Premises+and+Motifs+in+Renaissance+Thought+and+Literature&amp;rft.pub=Princeton&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.isbn=0-691-06505-5&amp;rft.aulast=Patrides&amp;rft.aufirst=C.+A.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAngels+in+Christianity" class="Z3988"></span></li>
